    tldr: "Parafarmacie offer specialized cosmetics, skincare, and wellness products in Italy. Understanding the difference between a farmacia and parafarmacia helps expats navigate Italian beauty and health products effectively.",
    metaDescription: "Guide to Italian parafarmacie and pharmacy cosmetics. Learn what to buy where and discover Italian skincare brands that expats love.",
    keywords: ["parafarmacia Italy", "Italian pharmacy cosmetics", "farmacia skincare products", "Italian beauty brands", "pharmacy cosmetics Italy", "parafarmacia vs farmacia"],
