    <p>Energy-focused supplements often combine B vitamins with ginseng, guarana, or other stimulating herbs. These products support increased energy without the jitteriness of excessive caffeine. Many Italian parafarmacie offer B-complex supplements in injection form (B12 injections) for those with absorption problems or preferring this delivery method. Monthly B12 injections are increasingly popular among expats seeking energy support and overall wellness.</p>

