    <p>Italian culture has a strong tradition of herbal medicine, and parafarmacie stock traditional remedies alongside modern supplements. Chamomile (camomilla), lemon balm, and passionflower support relaxation and sleep. St. John's Wort (iperico) is used for mood support, though interactions with medications must be considered. Valerian root helps sleep quality without the dependency risks of pharmaceutical sleep aids. Milk thistle (cardo mariano) supports liver health. These herbal supplements reflect Italian values appreciating natural healing approaches.</p>
