    <p>Individual mineral supplements address specific deficiencies or support particular health needs. Calcium supplementation is recommended for women, especially post-menopausal, supporting bone health. Calcium combined with vitamin D enhances absorption and effectiveness. Various forms exist—calcium citrate is better absorbed than calcium carbonate—allowing selection based on individual tolerance and preferences. Dosing often spans multiple daily doses, as absorption diminishes above 500 mg per dose.</p>
