<p>Imiquimod is a topical immunomodulator available by prescription in Italian pharmacies that enhances local immune response against HPV-infected cells. Applied topically three times weekly, it's effective for genital warts and sometimes for other wart types. Treatment duration varies; some warts resolve within weeks, others require months. Imiquimod is less effective for common warts on hands and feet but sometimes used when other treatments fail.</p>
