    tldr: "Know how to respond to mental health crises in Italy. Learn emergency contacts, crisis services, and hospitalization procedures for acute psychiatric emergencies.",
    metaDescription: "Guide to mental health emergencies and crisis services in Italy. Find emergency hotlines, psychiatric hospitalization, and immediate help for suicidal thoughts or severe mental health crises.",
